# ITMS Test Plan & Scenarios

This document outlines scenarios to verify that the core timetable features and Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) are functioning correctly.

## 1. Authentication & Session Management

| ID | Scenario | Steps to Reproduce | Expected Result |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| AUTH-01 | Successful Login | 1. Navigate to `/login`<br>2. Enter valid credentials<br>3. Click Login | Redirects to `/` (Dashboard). Session context is populated with user profile and role. |
| AUTH-02 | Invalid Login | 1. Navigate to `/login`<br>2. Enter invalid credentials<br>3. Click Login | Displays "Invalid login credentials" (or similar Supabase error). Remains on `/login`. |
| AUTH-03 | Sign Up defaults to Student | 1. Navigate to `/login`<br>2. Switch to Sign Up<br>3. Create a new account | Account is created. The database trigger automatically assigns the `student` role in the `profiles` table. |
| AUTH-04 | Protected Routes (Unauthenticated) | 1. Clear session data (Log out).<br>2. Attempt to navigate directly to `/project/123`. | Redirected back to `/login`. |
| AUTH-05 | Sign Out | 1. Log in to the application.<br>2. Click 'Sign Out' on Dashboard. | Session is cleared. Redirected to `/login`. |

