## Testing Instructions (For Local Development)

Since we are currently utilizing the **Auth Bypass**, you can test the RBAC frontend states by modifying the hardcoded user role in `src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx`.

1. Open `src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx`.
2. Locate the `bypassProfile` definition.
3. Change the `role` property from `'super_admin'` to `'student'`, `'faculty'`, or `'department_admin'`.
4. Save the file and reload the application.
5. Execute the relevant test scenarios assigned to that role.
